import { Dashboard } from '@material-ui/icons'
import React from 'react'
import { Router, Route } from 'react-router'
import BuySave from './pages/BuySave'
import EShop from './pages/EShop'
import Otp from './pages/Otp'
import Register from './pages/Register'
import Welcome from './pages/Welcome'
import CreateYourOwnPlan from './pages/CreateYourOwnPlan'

const Routes = () => (
  <Router>
    <Route exact path='/' component={Welcome} />
    <Route exact path='/verify-otp' component={Otp} />
    <Route exact path='/register' component={Register} />
    <Route exact path='/welcome' component={Dashboard} />
    <Route exact path='/subscribe' component={BuySave} />
    <Route exact path='/shop-gold' component={EShop} />
    <Route exact path='/create-your-own-plan' component={CreateYourOwnPlan} />
  </Router>
)

export default Routes
